HEADWORD: Bastardly
<hw>Bas"tard*ly</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Bastardlike; baseborn;
spurious; corrupt.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> -- <def2><pos>adv.</pos>
<def>In the manner of a bastard; spuriously.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark></def2> <rj><au>Shak. Donne.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
